  "name": "Aloe striata",
  "description": "Aloe striata is a small, stemless, evergreen, perennial, succulent, aloe species that naturally occurs on rocky slopes in coastal and semi-desert areas over the southern parts South Africa.<br>Aloe striata grows &gt;45 cm tall and &gt; 60 cm wide. The plant has a rosette of a few flat, broad, pale grey-green-pinkish leaves that vary in colour depending on the amount of sunlight. The leaves have a smooth, transparent, pink margin and subtle dark narrow lines running longitudinally. <br>Clusters of coral-red flowers appear on 60 cm tall stems during spring. Up to three branched inflorescences can arise from a single rosette. Offsets will appear around the base and form a small colony.<br><br><a href=\"http://ketenewplymouth.peoplesnetworknz.info/image_files/0000/0012/6463/Aloe_striata__Coral_Aloe_.JPG\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://ketenewplymouth.peoplesnetworknz.info/image_files/0000/0012/6463/Aloe_striata__Coral_Aloe_.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"auto\"></a><br></p> <p><a href=\"http://ketenewplymouth.peoplesnetworknz.info/image_files/0000/0012/6478/Aloe_striata__Coral_Aloe_-001.JPG\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://ketenewplymouth.peoplesnetworknz.info/image_files/0000/0012/6478/Aloe_striata__Coral_Aloe_-001.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"auto\"></a><br><br><a href=\"http://ketenewplymouth.peoplesnetworknz.info/image_files/0000/0012/6473/Aloe_striata__Coral_Aloe_-004.JPG\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://ketenewplymouth.peoplesnetworknz.info/image_files/0000/0012/6473/Aloe_striata__Coral_Aloe_-004.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"auto\"></a></p> <p>The green seed capsules<br><a href=\"http://ketenewplymouth.peoplesnetworknz.info/image_files/0000/0012/6468/Aloe_striata__Coral_Aloe_-003.JPG\"><img src=\"http://ketenewplymouth.peoplesnetworknz.info/image_files/0000/0012/6468/Aloe_striata__Coral_Aloe_-003.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"auto\"></a><br><br>Thanks to Wikipedia for text and information <a href=\"http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/3.0/\">http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/3.0/</a></p> <br style=\"clear:both;\"> <div class=\"hr\"> </div> ",
